OL,3,CMuslims and non-Muslims invited to
OL,4,Ccreate 'one-of-a kind' Quran manuscript
OL,6,FPeople in are being invited to create
OL,7,Fa new Quran manuscript as part of a
OL,8,Fproject exploring the city's
OL,9,Fconnection to the holy book.
OL,11,FMuslims and non-Muslims will have the
OL,12,Fchance to copy and transcribe some of
OL,13,Fthe 6,000 verses onto special
OL,14,Fcalligraphy paper.
OL,16,FBirmingham is home to the famous
OL,17,FBirmingham Quran manuscript, one of
OL,18,Fthe earliest manuscripts of the book
OL,19,Fwhich can be found at the Cadbury
OL,20,FResearch Library at the University of
OL,21,FBirmingham.
