OL,3,CMuslims and non-Muslims invited to
OL,4,Ccreate 'one-of-a kind' Quran manuscript
OL,6,FAs part of the project, which has been
OL,7,Fcreated by Museum of Islamic Arts &
OL,8,FHeritage (MIAH) Foundation and Culture
OL,9,FForward, workshops will take place at
OL,10,FMIAH Foundation's Islamic Arts Gallery
OL,11,Fin Balsall Heath.
OL,13,FAttendees will be able to learn about
OL,14,Fthe many different types of Arabic
OL,15,Fcalligraphy featured in Quran
OL,16,Fmanuscripts over the centuries through
OL,17,Fan exhibition on the history of the
OL,18,Fbook and the art of calligraphy.
