OL,6,FDr Neelam Hussain, Director of the
OL,7,FMIAH Foundation and Curator of Middle
OL,8,FEastern Manuscripts at the Cadbury
OL,9,FResearch Library, said: "It will be a
OL,10,FQuran by the city of Birmingham and
OL,11,Ffrom the people of Birmingham.
OL,13,F"The tradition of copying the Quran
OL,14,Fhas been there since revelation. There
OL,15,Fhave been Quran manuscripts across
OL,16,FChina and Sub-Saharan Africa for
OL,17,Fexample over 7-20th century, so we are
OL,18,Fkeeping the handwritten tradition
OL,19,Falive.
