OL,3,CMuslims and non-Muslims invited to
OL,4,Ccreate 'one-of-a kind' Quran manuscript
OL,6,F"Now it is Birmingham in the 21st
OL,7,Fcentury, so we are asking everyone
OL,8,Ffrom Muslims to non-Muslims to
OL,9,Fparticipate and continue this
OL,10,Ftradition copying with the rest of
OL,11,FBirmingham."
OL,13,F'Something one of a kind'
OL,15,FProfessor Sara Jones, Interim Academic
OL,16,FDirector of Culture Forward, said:
OL,17,F"Culture Forward aims to increase
OL,18,Fengagement with our rare and precious
OL,19,Fcultural collections, such as the
OL,20,FBirmingham Quran.
