OL,3,CMuslims and non-Muslims invited to
OL,4,Ccreate 'one-of-a kind' Quran manuscript
OL,6,F"This project is a big part of our
OL,7,FQuran in the City programme, and
OL,8,Fprovides people across Birmingham an
OL,9,Fopportunity to create something one of
OL,10,Fa kind for the city to treasure."
OL,12,FThe project began during Ramadan and
OL,13,Fcomes to an end on 1 June. The MIAH
OL,14,FIslamic Arts Gallery is holding
OL,15,Fregular workshops every Saturday 12-
OL,16,F2pm in Balsall Heath, for those aged
OL,17,F11+.
OL,19,FThe exhibition is open on Thursdays
OL,20,Fand Fridays 12pm-6pm and Saturdays 2pm-
OL,21,F6pm.
